# Tollway Example Configuration
#
# Generate a testnet keypair at: https://lab.stellar.org/account/create
# Fund it at: https://lab.stellar.org/account/fund
# Get testnet USDC at: https://faucet.circle.com (select Stellar Testnet)

# The Stellar secret key for the PAYING wallet (client side)
STELLAR_PRIVATE_KEY=S...your_testnet_secret_key...

# The Stellar public key for the RECEIVING wallet (server side)
STELLAR_PAY_TO=G...your_testnet_public_key...
